            "title": "買家主動求購山頂御峯 複式4房戶1億沽 呎價4.2萬丨恒隆持有收租逾20年 去年擲7億元為全幢升級翻新",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">樓市回暖，發展商加快拆售手頭收租物業。恒隆地產持有山頂豪宅<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"「御峯」\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:「御峯」;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4mO3OU9\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">「御峯」</a>收租逾20年，繼去年2月以1.6228億元售出47樓A室後，近日再以1億元售出15樓B室複式單位，為項目第二宗轉手個案。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更多消息：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga=\"{&quot;yLinkElement&quot;:&quot;context_link&quot;,&quot;yModuleName&quot;:&quot;content-canvas&quot;,&quot;yLinkText&quot;:&quot;恒地「開綠燈」拆售「皇帝女」山頂御峯6伙索價1.1億起｜半年內多個港島出租項目轉為拆售 灣仔Queen'&quot;}\" data-ylk=\"slk:恒地「開綠燈」拆售「皇帝女」山頂御峯6伙索價1.1億起｜半年內多個港島出租項目轉為拆售 灣仔Queen's Cube火速沽清;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/44NmBqZ\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">恒地「開綠燈」拆售「皇帝女」山頂御峯6伙索價1.1億起｜半年內多個港島出租項目轉為拆售 灣仔Queen's Cube火速沽清</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"前中國女首富時隔12年再入市 斥1.6億買西半山天御4房 涉逾千萬豪宅稅\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:前中國女首富時隔12年再入市 斥1.6億買西半山天御4房 涉逾千萬豪宅稅;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4e6JL0W\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">前中國女首富時隔12年再入市 斥1.6億買西半山天御4房 涉逾千萬豪宅稅</a></p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4c85d86d-2792-364a-83e0-29812e14319b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">是次售出的15樓B室複式單位，實用面積2,337方呎，採4房雙套房設計，客飯廳樓底高約6米，坐擁維港及跑馬地馬場雙重景觀，氣派非凡，獲買家主動提出購買意向及出價，最終以折實價1億元成交，折實呎價約42,790元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">御峯位於司徒拔道41C號，屬單幢式豪宅，提供54個單位，由恒隆地產於1995年以8.6億元投地，並於2002年落成後作招租用途，至今放租超過20年，恒隆地產在2025年擲7億元為全幢升級翻新。恒隆地產表示，現時項目策略以租賃為主，今年初以月租30萬元租出49樓A室。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"28Hse網站租盤\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qsEnY5782aEXxhoMmKjl8Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/d0f7466b5926d975b97d7526022583c0\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">28Hse網站租盤</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">28Hse網站租盤</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">翻查28Hse網站資料，御峯現時共1個中層及1個高層複式<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"單位放租\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:單位放租;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/3QtkbJJ\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">單位放租</a>，均採4房3浴室間隔，連車位，可眺望維港及跑馬地景觀，實用面積由2,375至2,390呎，均叫租每月28萬元，呎租逾117元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"天御\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:天御;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/天御-33415\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">天御</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"御峯\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:御峯;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/御峯-33491\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">御峯</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"西半山\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:西半山;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/西半山-27337\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">西半山</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"跑馬地\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:跑馬地;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/跑馬地-27344\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">跑馬地</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"山頂\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:山頂;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/山頂-27336\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">山頂</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"灣仔\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:灣仔;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/灣仔